    <item>
      <title>前将军普拉博沃宣布就任印度尼西亚总统胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/prabowo-takes-early-lead-in-unofficial-indonesia-vote-count</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度尼西亚国防部长普拉博沃·苏比安托 (Prabowo Subianto) 援引独立民意调查机构的话说，在周三的总统选举中宣布获胜，这使他在两次失败的尝试后有望成为东南亚最大经济体的领导者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/prabowo-takes-early-lead-in-unofficial-indonesia-vote-count</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 08:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人索齐赢回桑托斯腾出的纽约州众议院席位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/democrat-suozzi-wins-new-york-house-race-ap-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[民主党人汤姆·索齐(Tom Suozzi)赢得了竞选，接替了被赶下台的纽约众议员乔治·桑托斯(George Santos)，重新夺回了他之前占据的席位，并缩小了共和党在美国众议院的微弱多数席位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-14/democrat-suozzi-wins-new-york-house-race-ap-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 14 Feb 2024 03:04:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
